title: Blinkenpoi Assembly Party
subtitle: Blinkenpoi Assembly Day #3 10:30
description:
We build Blinkenpois
Come build a Blinkenpoi!overflo (DECT 6837, the dude with the donkey hat) will build Blinkenpois with you and guide you trough the process.There is documentation available online.[https://metalab.at/wiki/Blinkenpoi metalab WIKI][https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9AM9bLseyD4  Instruction video]You have a seat in the workshop if you got a Blinkenpoi kit before the Workshop.It is easy to build, expect 15 minutes to assemble a Blinkenpoi.
